Welcome to the Entrepreneurship Ecosystem Map: Your Home for All Your UW Entrepreneurial Needs!

This is a comprehensive, interactive map of all the entrepreneurial resources the University of Waterloo offers on-campus. The map individually targets your needs, whether you search under a specific category or use our timeline to display the resources that align with each stage in your entrepreneurial journey.

This website is a great place to discover new and upcoming resources and learning about where they reside on campus!
